	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The N64 is orders of magnitude more complex than the NES/SNES so that's going to impede the development of hardware clones. It's also quite a bit less popular, so there's a smaller market for it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


