		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The chip was made by SGI if my memory is good so compared to a nes/snes/genesis clone, I don't see how they could make something on the cheap for that. When it came out, the psx was all the rage (Psone is the new name but let's forget about the pedantic thing) so the N64 maybe doesn't ahve the same scope of popularity as their previous console.<br /><br />So my guess would be that it will be quite unlikely that they make a clone of it, if ever.

		

		</td>
